# ---------- Monorepo root .gitignore (Frontend + Backend) ----------

# === Angular / Node (frontend) ===
FrontEnd-EmployeeManagement/node_modules/
FrontEnd-EmployeeManagement/dist/
FrontEnd-EmployeeManagement/.angular/
FrontEnd-EmployeeManagement/coverage/
FrontEnd-EmployeeManagement/*.log

# === Spring Boot / Maven (backend) ===
EmployeeManagementSystems/target/
EmployeeManagementSystems/.mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar
EmployeeManagementSystems/*.log
hs_err_pid*

# === Editors / IDE (any folder) ===
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.iml
**/.settings/
**/.classpath
**/.project

# === OS junk ===
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# === Local config / secrets (keep application.properties tracked) ===
**/*.local.*
**/application-local.properties
**/application-*.properties.local
**/application-*.yml.local

# === Generic build caches (just in case) ===
**/build/
**/out/

# === Misc logs ===
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
